      "type": "text",
      "x": 605,
      "y": 330,
      "width": 263,
      "height": 388,
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "FillState (useReducer)\n• values: FormValues\n• touched: Set<fieldId>\n• isSubmitted: boolean\n• errors: Map<fieldId, string>\n\nOn mount:\n• init values from schema\n• apply prefillToday fields\n\nOnChange:\n→ ConditionalLogicEngine\n→ CalculationEngine\n→ rerender with new state\n\nOn SUBMIT:\n→ validateAllVisible\n→ strip hidden fields\n→ build FormResponse\n→ localStorage",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "FillState (useReducer)\n• values: FormValues\n• touched: Set<fieldId>\n• isSubmitted: boolean\n• errors: Map<fieldId, string>\n\nOn mount:\n• init values from schema\n• apply prefillToday fields\n\nOnChange:\n→ ConditionalLogicEngine\n→ CalculationEngine\n→ rerender with new state\n\nOn SUBMIT:\n→ validateAllVisible\n→ strip hidden fields\n→ build FormResponse\n→ localStorage",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "aA",
      "id": "ygGWaBckVCEwlgHwU0mox",
      "autoResize": true
    },
